	<name>4KWALL</name>
	<summary>Set 4K, HD and live wallpapers for your desktop background</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>
		4kWall is a fast wallpaper manager and changer for Linux. Browse, download,
		and set stunning 4K, UHD, and HD wallpapers as your desktop background in a
		single click, with thousands of high-resolution images to choose from.
	  </p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
	  <ul>
		<li>Browse and search a huge wallpaper catalogue with live filtering</li>
		<li>One-click wallpaper setting on GNOME and Wayland</li>
		<li>Automatic wallpaper changer with sequential and random slideshow modes</li>
		<li>Per-monitor wallpapers for multi-monitor and dual-screen setups</li>
		<li>Built-in viewer with zoom, rotation, and crossfade transitions</li>
		<li>Organise backgrounds into Favorites and manage Downloads offline</li>
		<li>Search wallpapers by colour and batch-download in parallel</li>
		<li>Clean dark interface with system-tray support</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>
